{"serial": "44011", "department_serial": 43, "code": "EC3112", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Public Economics", "ch": "公共經濟學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Yun-Min"], "ch": ["陳韻旻"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "306"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "經濟學系", "en": "Department of Economics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 4, "selected": 68, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "財政學是一門研究政府經濟行為的學科，分析政府的支出與收入政策對經濟體系所產生的效果，並加以評估政策的有效性。本學期的課程先從討論政府角色與政府的配置功能出發，其中涵蓋市場失靈、公共財的提供以及矯正外部效果等主題。接著進一步說明公共選擇理論，了解利益團體對政策的影響。最後介紹公共支出的計畫評估方法、現況以及政府如何透過公共支出發揮分配功能，其中包含針對所得重分配、社會福利、社會保險等政策議題。", "en": "Public Economics studies government economic behavior, analyzing the effects of government spending and tax policies on the economy and evaluating the effectiveness of those policies. This course begins with a discussion on the role of government and its allocative functions, covering topics such as market failure, public goods provision, and correcting for externalities. It then explains public choice theory and examines the influence of interest groups on policy. Finally, the course introduces methods for evaluation of public expenditure, discusses the current state of public expenditure, and explores how the government performs its allocative function, including policy issues such as income redistribution and social security."}, "outline": {"ch": "Course OutlineWeekTopicNote\n1  福利經濟學的回顧──效率與公平概念的介紹\n2  市場失靈\n3  聯合消費\n4  聯合消費\n5  外部效果\n6  外部效果\n7  公共選擇\n8  公共選擇\n9  期中考\n10  公營事業與非營利事業組織\n11  公共支出計畫評估\n12  公共支出計畫評估\n13  公共支出分析\n14 所得重分配的支出政策\n15  社會福利與社會保險支出\n16 社會福利與社會保險支出\n17  期末考", "en": "Course OutlineWeekTopicNote\n1  Welfare Economics\n2  Market Failure\n3  Public Goods\n4  Public Goods\n5  Externalities\n6  Externalities\n7  Public Choice\n8  Public Choice\n9  Midterm Exam\n10 Public Sector Pricing\n11 Public Sector Pricing\n12 Cost-Benefit Analysis\n13 Cost-Benefit Analysis\n14 Government Expenditure\n15 Income Redistribution\n16 Social Security\n17 Social Security\n18 Final Exam"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Course Material徐偉初、歐俊男、謝文盛，2020，財政學（5版），台北：華泰。\nOther MaterialRosen,Harvey S. and Ted Gayer, Public Finance,10th Edition,2014\nGruber, Jonathan, Public Finance and Public Policy, 5th Edition, 2015", "en": "Course Material徐偉初、歐俊男、謝文盛，2020，財政學（5版），台北：華泰。\nOther MaterialRosen,Harvey S. and Ted Gayer, Public Finance,10th Edition,2014\nGruber, Jonathan, Public Finance and Public Policy, 5th Edition, 2015"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席率 20％\n期中考 40％\n期末考 40％", "en": "Class Participation 20％\nMidterm Exam 40％\nFinal Exam 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "by appointment", "en": "by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "檢討考卷", "en": "Flex supplement teaching week"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科\n\n\n、\n\n\n財政金融", "en": "基礎學科\n\n\n、\n\n\n財政金融"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "永續發展", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Global Perspective", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Attendance/Perform